option at $22.3505 per share using a binomial option-pricing model. Each bond is convertible into 26.185 shares of Larson’s
common stock, so the total fair value of the embedded derivative is
$585.25 per bond ($22.3505 per share multiplied by 26.185 shares per
bond).
                <footnote id="aag-afi9_fn6" label="fn 6" role="number">
